				<div class="entry-meta">
			<a href="https://leilashami.wordpress.com/2017/03/27/en-siria-las-vidas-civiles-no-importan/" title="7:56 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2017-03-27T19:56:05+00:00" pubdate>March 27, 2017</time></a><span class="byline"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://leilashami.wordpress.com/author/leilashami/" title="View all posts by Leila Al Shami" rel="author">Leila Al Shami</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Publicado originalmente en <a href="https://hummusforthought.com/2017/03/26/in-syria-civilian-lives-dont-matter/" target="_blank">‘Hummus For Thought’</a> (Joey Husseini Ayoub Ed.)</p>
<p>Desde la llegada de Trump al poder se ha producido una importante escalada en la intervención estadounidense en Siria, supuestamente para derrotar al ISIS.</p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_819" style="max-width: 270px" class="wp-caption alignright"><img data-attachment-id="819" data-permalink="https://leilashami.wordpress.com/2017/03/27/in-syria-civilian-lives-dont-matter/c7hbz_tx0aesmqb/#main" data-orig-file="https://leilashami.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/c7hbz_tx0aesmqb.jpg?w=260&#038;h=173" data-orig-size="960,640" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="C7HBZ_TX0AEsMqB" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://leilashami.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/c7hbz_tx0aesmqb.jpg?w=260&#038;h=173?w=300" data-large-file="https://leilashami.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/c7hbz_tx0aesmqb.jpg?w=260&#038;h=173?w=644" class="  wp-image-819 alignright" src="https://leilashami.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/c7hbz_tx0aesmqb.jpg?w=260&#038;h=173" alt="C7HBZ_TX0AEsMqB" width="260" height="173" srcset="https://leilashami.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/c7hbz_tx0aesmqb.jpg?w=260&amp;h=173 260w, https://leilashami.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/c7hbz_tx0aesmqb.jpg?w=520&amp;h=346 520w, https://leilashami.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/c7hbz_tx0aesmqb.jpg?w=150&amp;h=100 150w, https://leilashami.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/c7hbz_tx0aesmqb.jpg?w=300&amp;h=200 300w" sizes="(max-width: 260px) 100vw, 260px" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Voluntarios de los Cascos Blancos &#8211; Jina, Alepo</p></div>
<p>Los Estados Unidos ya tienen cientos de efectivos de sus Fuerzas Especiales luchando en el terreno junto a las Fuerzas Democráticas de Siria y les dan respaldo con centenares de ataques aéreos. Ahora se ha desplegado una unidad de artillería de los Marines y se planea enviar más tropas de tierra. <a href="https://leilashami.wordpress.com/2017/03/27/en-siria-las-vidas-civiles-no-importan/#more-847" class="more-link">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></p>
